    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel the <strong>cooled eggs</strong></p><p>Add a <strong>peeled egg</strong> to the centre of each <strong>veggie mixture circle</strong></p><p>Wrap the veggie mixture around each peeled egg and seal it tightly on all sides so that there aren't any gaps – these are your <strong>veggie-coated eggs</strong></p>",
