    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong> and <strong>nigella seeds</strong> to a plate with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and give it a good mix up – these are your <strong>nigella breadcrumbs</strong></p><p>Add a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable</strong> <strong>oil</strong> to a separate plate</p><p>Turn the<strong> veggie-coated eggs</strong> in the <strong>vegetable</strong> <strong>oil</strong>, shake off the excess, then add them to the <strong>nigella breadcrumbs</strong> and press firmly until they're evenly coated all over – these are your<strong> breaded eggs</strong></p>",
